attributes.Long form description: The student assembles a piece of furniture. He first inspects the pieces and takes each of them to understand how to put them together. After a few tries and with the instructions of the instructor, he takes the legs of the stool, assembles them correctly, takes the bolt and the hex nut to screw the base, and tightens the bolt with the wrench. He continues to inspect the seat to assemble it to the legs of the furniture, he takes the screw and saddle washer to screw each of the four legs. In the end, he grabs the stool and puts it on the table to finish.
